section.section:
A citation shall contain:
The name and address of the registered owner alleged to be liable under this section;
The registration number of the motor vehicle involved in such violation;
The location where such violation took place;
The date and time of such violation;
The amount of the toll not paid;
The amount of the civil penalty; and
The date by which the toll and penalty must be paid.

text.section:
Adjudication of liability under this section:
Shall be based upon a preponderance of evidence;
May not be deemed a conviction of a registered owner of a motor vehicle under the Motor Vehicle Code;
May not be made part of the registered owner's motor vehicle operating record; and
May not be considered in the provision of motor vehicle insurance coverage.
